N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 26.1 - Purchases

State Regulations

No holder of an AP permit shall purchase or agree to
purchase any alcohol from any person, who is not duly licensed to sell and
distribute alcohol at the time of such agreement and sale. Notes
